Step 6: Create Display Status Column

Create a calculated column in:

DagInventory
Display Status =
VAR RunCount =
    COUNTROWS(
        RELATEDTABLE(AuditToday)
    )
RETURN
IF(
    RunCount = 0,
    "NOT STARTED",
    MAXX(
        RELATEDTABLE(AuditToday),
        AuditToday[dag_status]
    )
)

Expected output:

DAG	Status
dag_oscar_LRA	NOT STARTED
dag_customer	COMPLETED
dag_sales	FAILED

⸻

Step 7: Create Duration Measure

Duration Minutes =
VAR StartTime =
    MAX(AuditToday[dag_start_time])
VAR EndTime =
    MAX(AuditToday[dag_end_time])
VAR Status =
    MAX(AuditToday[dag_status])
RETURN
SWITCH(
    TRUE(),
    Status = "IN PROGRESS",
        DATEDIFF(
            StartTime,
            NOW(),
            MINUTE
        ),
    Status = "COMPLETED",
        DATEDIFF(
            StartTime,
            EndTime,
            MINUTE
        ),
    Status = "FAILED",
        DATEDIFF(
            StartTime,
            EndTime,
            MINUTE
        ),
    BLANK()
)

